<subSubSection id="C337088DF757B116B182FE0030D241EB" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F757B116B182FE0031DD41C7" blockId="34.[151,1436,403,789]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">
<materialsCitation id="3B45515BF757B116B182FE0031E641C7" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3766756309" collectingDate="1854-08-14" collectionCode="TYPE" country="Sweden" location="The" municipality="Onanis River" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" specimenCount="1" typeStatus="holotype">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F757B116B182FE0032C24154" box="[199,251,511,537]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: Wahlberg’s (1855: 213) description gives no information on how many specimens he had at hand. From Sundevall’s manuscript catalogues it is apparent that the description was probably based on a single specimen—at least, only 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF757B116B0F5FDB830704123" box="[432,585,583,609]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
seems to have been sent to 
<collectingCountry id="F33A1B96F757B116B238FDB831E04123" box="[893,985,583,609]" name="Sweden" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">Sweden</collectingCountry>
. 
<location id="8EF20DDDF757B116B2A7FDB836374123" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F757B116B1D2FEB536C84057:8EF20DDDF757B116B2A7FDB836374123" box="[994,1038,583,609]" country="Sweden" municipality="Onanis River" name="The" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">The</location>
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F757B116B551FDB836404123" box="[1044,1145,583,609]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">holotype</typeStatus>
, NRM 558942 [11695], is a study skin of an adult male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F757B116B309FD9430C741C7" box="[588,766,618,645]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" value="1854-08-14">
<collectingDate id="EFD7842EF757B116B309FD9430C741C7" box="[588,766,618,645]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" value="1854-08-14">14 August 1854</collectingDate>
</date>
at the 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BF6C17CF757B116B20CFD9431E641C7" box="[841,991,619,645]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">Onanis River</collectingMunicipality>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B925B06F757B116B182FD7030D241EB" blockId="34.[151,1436,403,789]" box="[199,747,655,681]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">
<materialsCitation id="3B45515BF757B116B182FD7030DF41EB" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3766756344" box="[199,742,655,681]" collectionCode="VERIFIED" country="Namibia" location="Onanis River" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" specimenCount="1" typeStatus="holotype">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F757B116B182FD70331A41E4" box="[199,291,655,681]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">VERIFIED</collectionCode>
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F757B116B06FFD69336241E4" box="[298,347,662,678]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">TYPE</typeStatus>
LOCALITY: 
<location id="8EF20DDDF757B116B091FD70304B41EB" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F757B116B1D2FEB536C84057:8EF20DDDF757B116B091FD70304B41EB" box="[468,626,655,681]" country="Namibia" name="Onanis River" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">Onanis River</location>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F33A1B96F757B116B338FD7030DF41EB" box="[637,742,655,681]" name="Namibia" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">Namibia</collectingCountry>
