</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C337088DF757B116B182FD4C36C84057" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F757B116B182FD4C36C84057" blockId="34.[151,1436,403,789]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555">
COMMENTS: There is no entry in the journal for this date and place. Wahlberg collected a number of specimens in 
<date id="FF937DC6F757B116B1BBFD2833A241B3" box="[254,411,726,753]" pageId="34" pageNumber="555" value="1854-08">August 1854</date>
. The localities on labels are interspersed with Onanis and Swakop rivers. Specimens collected from 14–19 August are labelled Onanis River, so the TL can be confirmed as correct.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
